title: Bonus Episode: Murder in the Mountains Update
description:
A breaking update in the case involving the 1982 murders of Annette Schnee and Bobbi Jo Oberholzer. A major development in this 39-year-old unsolved, double homicide case. You can find our original episode at https://anatomyofmurder.com/murder-in-the-mountains/

Bonus Episode recorded March 3, 2020.

For episode information and photos, please visit https://anatomyofmurder.com/
